<plot>Between 1939 and 2002, black actors and actresses received a combined total of 39 Academy Award nominations - only a handful made the odyssey to the podium to possess the Golden Man. Towering African-American talents speak for the first time on the labyrinthine twists and turns of OSCAR'S BLACK ODYSSEY.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?416406</url></doc>
